> Happy Weekend SMS
> Happy Weekend greeting cards
> Happy Weekend quotes
> Happy Weekend Wishes

> Latest/Updated Collection - Happy Weekend Wishes mobile application provide you latest collection of greeting cards, GIF Images and Quotes Messages. We keep you updated, Time to time we keep on adding new greeting cards to deliver you best app experience with the nice and updated collection.

> Offline Support Feature – Once you open an greeting card or quotes then you can check out the same later without using your internet connection, that will be stored/cached locally and never use your internet data for browsing same greeting card. so that you can revisit greeting card offline anytime.
